00:04:48.551 --> 00:04:49.840
"Do automatic placements."

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:51.280
Why?

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:54.080
When we were being able to break down the results,

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:57.280
we were able to see that when you have

00:04:58.200 --> 00:04:59.880
all of these different placements,

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:04.360
you were actually able to spend a little bit,

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:08.040
it was spending something like 30 cents, 40 cents,

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:09.440
1 dollar. Okay?

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:11.920
And then it was spending all the other money

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:14.560
on the Facebook Feed or the Instagram Feed

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.880
and every representative was saying that

00:05:17.200 --> 00:05:19.520
"Yes, because it's optimizing towards those options,

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:22.080
so it's spending all this amount of money there."

00:05:22.440 --> 00:05:24.160
My way of thinking is this

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:27.080
what if this is a conspiracy, okay,

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:29.280
what if Facebook wants you to spend in

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:31.800
all of the placements, even if they know that

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:33.520
