00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:55.120
It's a lot of money as you can understand.

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:58.040
So this is one of the other things that it's really

00:05:58.040 --> 00:06:01.000
annoying and we will not be able to break down anymore.

